text: Þis his þære V hide boc æt dydelingtune þe eadred cing gebocode Wulfrice lis þegne on eche yrfe.
Þis syndon þa land gemæro into dydelingtune.
Arest on lindune easteweardre to þare hina gemære on cheoles burge eastgeat.
Þonon ut on þæt westgeat of þam westgeate on dydelingdune.
Up andlang winburnan oþ hore tuninge gemære.
Andlang hore tuninge gemæres oþ stigla pæþ of stigela paþe ofer þone readan weg þæt eft on lindune.
And þa men þe on þæm londee standeþ & seo mæd liþ on ige þe þær to gebyred.
